            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EYes they can. There are several vaccines that have been authorized by WHO and the Medicines Control Authority of Zimbabwe (MCAZ)  to vaccinate children 3 years and older. Vaccination of children 12-17 years old started in 2021 and 3-11 year olds in 2022. \u003C/p\u003E",
