            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EExercise helps your physical and emotional well-being. However, lockdowns and quarantines are challenging. If you enjoy dancing, play some music on your phone.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EPerhaps your children will dance with you, and help everyone feel better. Also, think about walks in your neighbourhood if that is possible. If you walk with your child, you can also talk about what you see, count cars, or do other “play-and-learn” activities.\u003C/p\u003E",
