            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EPregnancy is a powerful life experience for both women and men. One in 10 men has experience of perinatal depression. \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003ESigns of depression include physical, emotional, and changes in thinking and behaviour that last for more than two weeks. It is important to seek professional help as soon as possible. Talk to your doctor or health professional.\u003C/p\u003E",
