            "type": "FAQ",
            "question": "Mwana achangoberekwa anofanira kurara zvakadini?",
            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-27T07:57:57+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EFri, 02/27/2026 - 07:57\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-02T13:48:42+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EMon, 03/02/2026 - 13:48\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EMadiro ekurara anoitwa nevana anoshanduka pavanenge vachikura. Vana vachangozvarwa vanoda kurara nguva yakareba kupfuura vamwe. Vanowanzo rara kwenguva pfupi inosvika maawa 2 kusvika 3 pakati pekuyamwa, uye vanogona kurara maawa anosvika 14 kusvika 17 pazuva.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EMugore rekutanga, vana vadiki vanoda maawa 12 kusvika 15 ekurara asi mugore rechipiri inoderera kusvika kumaawa 14. Kune vana vane makore matatu kusvika mashanu, maawa 10 kusvika 13 ekurara anokurudzirwa.\u003C/p\u003E",
