            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-02T14:34:15+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EMon, 03/02/2026 - 14:34\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EMabhuku akakosha zvikuru pazera irori. Vana vane mhuri dzinoverenga navo zuva nezuva vane unyanzvi hwakakura hunodiwa kuti vabudirire muchikoro. Vana vane chido chokuverenga, vachada kudzidza kuverenga. Vana vari nani vanogona kuverenga, vanodzidza zviri nani uye vanobudirira zvikuru kuchikoro.\u003C/p\u003E",
