            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-02T13:59:38+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EMon, 03/02/2026 - 13:59\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EKana zvakakuomerai kutenga mabhuku, onai kuti mungaawana here kushamwari nevavakidzani vanogona kukugoverai mabhuku aisahndiswa nevana vavo kubva vachiri vadiki. Zvinogonekawo kugadzira mabhuku madiki akareruka, munogona kunyora mufananidzo wenyaya dzenyu, kana kutora mifananidzo kubva mumapepanhau kana magazini uye kugadzira nyaya kubva maari.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EKana mwana wenyu ane makore mana kana kupfuura, regai aite mifananidzo uye agadzire nyaya pamwe chete, iyo yamunogona kunyora pamifananidzo. Iri rinowanzova bhuku rinofarirwa nevana. Vana vanofarira kuverenga bhuku rimwe chete nguva nenguva, saka hamudi mabhuku akawandisa.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "chatbot_subcategory": 526,
            "related_article": 1851,
            "mandatory": 1
