            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-03T09:15:43+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 03/03/2026 - 09:15\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003ETangai pakarepo mwana paanongoberekwa! Chokwadi ndechekuti kunyange asati aberekwa, mwana anokwanisa kunzwa inzwi renyu uye pashure anozorirangarira kubva achiri mudumbu. Izwi rwenyu rinonyaradza mwana, uye mwana achangoberekwa anowanzo cheuka kwariri.\u003C/p\u003E",
