            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EHazvikurudzirwi kunonotsa hurongwa hwekupiwa nhomba. Nguva ipi neipi yamunononotsa kupihwa kwenhomba, munenge muchiwedzera mukana wekuti mwana wenyu abatwe nezvirwere zvakakomba.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EDzivisai njodzi uye teverai hurongwa hwenyika hweZimbabwe hwekupihwa kwenhomba kuitira kuchengetedza mwana wenyu asati asangana nechirwere chinotyisa chinogona kuisa upenyu panjodzi. \u003Cstrong\u003ERerai Umntwana Vaccination Tool\u003C/strong\u003E inokuzivisai kana nguva yekupihwa nhomba inotevera yasvika uye chinokubatsirai kutevera nhomba dzese dzinokurudzirwa.\u003C/p\u003E",
