            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-01-14T10:49:26+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EWed, 01/14/2026 - 10:49\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EMusati matora chero mushonga pamunenge muchiyamwisa, zvakanaka kuudza chiremba wenyu kuti muri kuyamwisa asati akupai chero mushonga wekurapwa. Chiremba wenyu achakupai ma antibiotics kana mimwe mishonga inorwisa utachiona asi muchiramba muchiyamwisa pese pazvinogoneka.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EImi munofanirwa kuve nechokwadi nachiremba wenyu kuti imi munogona kuyamwisa muchitora mushonga. \u003C/p\u003E",
