            "question": "Yiziphi izinto ezingancedisa umntwana ukuthi afunde engekhaya?",
            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-11T08:11:08+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EWed, 03/11/2026 - 08:11\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-17T09:54:05+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 03/17/2026 - 09:54\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003ELokho ovele ulakho ngekhaya kwanele ukwenza umntwana afunde loba engayanga esikolo sabantwana kumbe endaweni yokunakekelwa kwabantwana. Ngokwesibonelo, ngekhaya kule zinto ezincane ezinengi (izitsha zokudla, amasokisi, amahlamvu asesivandeni ) umntwana angazisebenzisa ukubala, ukuhlela izinto zibe ngamaqembu (beka ama- \u003Cem\u003Efork\u003C/em\u003E ndawonye lezipunu ndawonye), kanye lokusebenzisa ulimi ukuchaza (yiliphi ihlamvu elikhulu kulamanye, elihle kakhulu, elibomvu, njalo njalo\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EAbantwana  bangafunda kungela zinto zokusebenzisa, ngokuba yingxenye yalokho okwenziwa ngekhaya. Bangapheka lawe ukudla, kumbe bancedise esivandeni, kumbe bayethenga loyise ezitolo. Nxa ukhuluma labo ngalokhu abakubonileyo labakwenzileyo, wandisa amazwi abawaziyo njalo ubanceda ukuthi balungele isikolo.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "chatbot_subcategory": 561,
