            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EAwudingi ukuchitha imali enengi ukuze unike umntwana isiqalo esihle empilweni  Zinengi izinto ongazenza ezinganceda umntwana  kodwa zingadingi mali.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003ENgokwesibonelo, awudingi mali ukuze uxoxe lomntwana ngesikhathi  ulungisa ukudla, usebenza  loba uhlanza ingekhaya. Ufundisa umntwana ngaso sonke isikhathi ,umzuzu ngomzuzu!\u003C/p\u003E",
