            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EOkokuqala, sicela ukhumbule ukuthi “ukukhalipha” akusona kuphela isiqokoqela. Njengomzali, nceda umntwana abe lomusa njalo abe ngumuntu olothando obambisana labanye, ancede labo abalobunzima.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003ENjalo “ukukhalipha” akuphathelananga nje lokwazi amabala, ukubala inombolo kumbe ukubakwazi ukubala kulabanye; kuphinde kugoqele lokufunda okunengi ngempilo, njengokukhulumisana labanye, ukuxazulula inhlupho kanye lokufunda imizwa yakho. \u003C/p\u003E",
