            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EUmntwana, kuyo yonke iminyaka yokukhula, udinga ukunyakazisa umzimba  nsukuzonke. Abantwana badinga  ukunyaka, ukuzelula, ukusebenzisa ingalo lenyawo ukuze bafunde indawo abahlala kuyo (ngendlela engelangozi , lawe useduze). Abantwana asebekhulakhulile badinga indawo ezingela  ngozi  zokufundela ukukhasa, ukuhamba lokugijima.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EI-Rerai Umntwana Games ingakupha imibono yemisebenzi lemidlalo elula elingayijabulela ndawonye lomntwana. Ukukhula okulempilakahle komntwana kugoqela  ukukhula komzimba kanye lokwengqondo. Isikhathi sokwenza i-exercise yisikhathi  esisetshenziswe kuhle kakhulu!\u003C/p\u003E",
