            "type": "FAQ",
            "question": "Ingabe abantwana bami kufanele bazigqokise?",
            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-10T15:16:31+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 03/10/2026 - 15:16\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-17T09:48:30+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 03/17/2026 - 09:48\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EUkugqoka kuyinto eqakathekileyo okumele umntwana ayifunde, kodwa kungaba nzima. Kuyanceda ukuhlukanisa ukugqoka kuyenziwe kancane kancane. Ukufundisa inyathelo lokucina kuqala kungasebenza kuhle, ngoba kuvumela umntwana ukuthi azwe impumelelo kuqala, kuthuthukise ukuzethemba kwakhe, njalo kancane kancane aqeqeshe aze akwazi yonke inqubo yokugqoka. Khumbula ukuthi umntwana ngamunye uhlukile njalo uzafunda ngesikhathi esitshiyeneyo.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E“Ukuba kwazi ukuzenzela” kuqakathekile ekukhuleni kuhle. Labantwana abasesebancane bayakufuna ukuzama ukuzigqokela ingwane, amahembe, amasokisi kumbe ukuzikhumula! Zama ukukhuthaza lokhu kufunda. Kuyakha ukuzimela njalo kuncedisa umntwana ukuthi athuthukise ukusebenzisa izandla zakhe kuhle, njalo kuqakathekile kulokho okuzadingeka esikolo ngesikhathini esizayo\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
