            "question": "Ngiimelana njani lokukhathazeka ngomntwana okhubazekileyo?",
            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-10T15:11:08+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 03/10/2026 - 15:11\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-17T09:48:30+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 03/17/2026 - 09:48\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EAkulula njengomzali ukwamukela loba ukukhangelana lomntwana okhubazekileyo. Zizwe ukhululekile ukuveza indlela ozizwa ngayo ngakho futhi ubuze imibuzo ezakuncedisa uzwisise kangcono ngokukhubazeka komntwana lokuthi ungamsekela njani. Umntanakho njengabo bonke abantwana, engathuthuka ekukhuleni kwakhe lanxa nje  ekhubazekile njalo akulethele injabulo enkulu ekuphileni kwakho.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EIsigaba sezeluleko ku Rerai Umntwana silakho okunengi okungakuncedisa uzwisise ngcono ngokukhubazeka. Esigabeni seMidlalo, uzathola imibono eminengi yokuthi ungasekela njani ukukhula komntwana ngokuxhumana kwansuku zonke lokudlala. Abezempilakahle labo bengakusekela njalo baphendule imibuzo yakho eminengi. Ukwabelana labanye abazali abalabantwana abakhubazekileyo kungakuncedisa ukuthi ungakhathazeki njalo uthole okunye okungakuncedisa mayelana lalesi simo.\u003C/p\u003E",
