            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EMunyisa umntwana nxa efuna ukumunya njalo; yekela amunyeisikhathi eside asifunayo.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EVumela umntwana azisukele ebeleni ngaphambi kokumnika elinye. Lokhu kuyamnceda ukuthi athole uchago oluzamenza asuthe akholwe. Kunceda njalo ukuthi umntwana athole uchago olubuyela ekucineni olulokudla lemisoco.\u003C/p\u003E",
