            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003ENgobunengi abantwana bayenza amaphutha enkulumweni yabo kuminyaka embalwa yokuqala yokukhula kwenkulumo. Kodwa phose  emnyakeni wesithathu,  abantwana abanengi bayazwisiswa ngabondli babo ,abafowabo kanye labontanga. Nxa ukhathazekile ngokuthi  umntwana ulohlupho ekukhulumeni kwakhe ,cabangisisa ngokuthi  kukangaki abantu  abangamaziyo kangako umntwana abangazwisisiyo akukhulumayo? Lapho umntwana eseleminyaka  emibili, umuntu onganjwayelanga kufanele azwisise  phose  ingxenye eyodwa  kusiya  kwezintathu zalokho umntwana akutshoyo.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003ELapho  umntwana eleminyaka emithathu kusedlula , umuntu ongamjwayelanga kufanele azwisise okutshiwo ngumntwana  isikhathi esinengi,  loba nje kwesinye isikhathi umntwana uzakhuluma amabala lemisindo yamabala  athile ngendlela ehlukileyo kulabadala. Nxa ukhathazekile ( nxa umntwana ezwakala engakakhuli okuhambelana leminyaka yakhe , engazwisiseki,, ephangisa ukuthukuthela loba engezwa endlebeni i kuba  kuhle ukuxoxa ngezinto ezikukhathazwayo ngabezempilakahle . Bangakhuthaza njalo  ukuhlolwa okupheleleyo,kumbe batsho  ezinye indlela ezingakhuthaza ukuthi umntwana akhulume.\u003C/p\u003E",
