            "question": "Abantwana sebephangisa ukuhlatshwa amajekiseni  amanengi kakhulu yini? ",
            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-10T13:25:40+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 03/10/2026 - 13:25\u003C/time\u003E\n",
