            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003E Abantwana bathola amajekiseni okubavikela emikhuhlaneni eyingozi ngokuphangisa .Amajekiseni ezigabeni zokuqala zokuphila aqakatheke kakhulu ngoba avikela  abantwana  besasebancane lapho amasosha  omzimba engakenziwa ngokugcweleyo. Imithi yokuvikela imikhuhlane eminengi ngeke iwuhlukuluze umzimba womntwana.\u003C/p\u003E",
