            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-17T09:54:05+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 03/17/2026 - 09:54\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EUkudlala kungaba yindlela enhle kakhulu yokupholisa, ukukhula, ukufunda, lokuxhumana kwakho lomntwana. Isibonelo,  umntwana uyabakwazi ukuthi  kuyini akuthandayo lalokho angakuthandiyo  ngokudlala \u003Cem\u003E(sensory play\u003C/em\u003E) lokuthuthukisa ama \u003Cem\u003Efine motor skills\u003C/em\u003E ngendela ethokozisayo engela ngozi\u003Cem\u003E.\u003C/em\u003E Ungathola ukuthi  umntwana uthatha isikhathi eside ukuthi athakazelele okwenziwa ngabanye abantwana abangakhubazekanga.Nxa kunjalo, zama ukuba lesineke njalo unanzelele izitshengiselo zokuthi  umntwana  uyathakazelela  okwenziwayo\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EKungadingeka ukuthi umtshengise i-toy entsha kanengi nengi andubana ayilandele ngamehlo njalo azame ukuyifinyelela. Kodwa intuthuko iyenzeka, futhi uyingxenye eqakathekileyo yokukhula kwakhe! Xhumana labezempilakahle udinge izixwayiso mayelana lemidlalo umntwana angayithakazelela engamncedisa ekukhuleni kwakhe  Isibonelo,  nxa umntwana elobunzima bokusebenzisa izandla,imidlalo lapho ofihla khona izinto futhi umkhuthaze ukuthi azithole (ngaphansi komqamelo njengesibonelo)  ingamkhuthaza ukusebenzisa izandla zakhe ukuze adobhe izinto.\u003C/p\u003E",
