            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-17T09:54:05+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 03/17/2026 - 09:54\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EYebo kunjalo! Eqinisweni, abantwana balethuba elihle lokufunda ukukhuluma indimi eziphezu kolimi olulodwa. Ulwazi lwendimi ezinengi  lolu luzabanceda ekuthuthukeni kwabo esikhathini esizayo. Mhlawumbe ulamabhuku alula ngolimi lwakho lwasekhaya. Ungawabalela abantwana kumbe ubaxoxele izindaba ngolimi lolu.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003ELangabe esikolo umntwana efunda ngolunye ulimi ,ngoncedo  lwakho, bayafunda ukuthi amabhuku lezindaba, indlela yokuxoxa indaba, indlela yokubuza lokuphendula imibuzo, njalo njalo. Njengoba abantwana bakho beqala isikolo, nxa sebelisekelo esihle solimini  lwasekhaya kanye lesiko lakho, ngeke babe lodubo ukufunda ulimi olutsha kusikhathi esizayo.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
