            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-17T09:54:05+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 03/17/2026 - 09:54\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003ELapho abantwana beqala ukuba lamazinyo, ngezinye izikhathi yilapho bezama khona ukuluma, ngitsho lalapho bemunya! Nxa  kuyinkinga leyo, ungafaka umunwe phakathi, uncindezele,  njalo ukhulume , “Ungalumi ! umntwana  kakwazi  ukuthi kubuhlungu. Abantwana abaleminyaka engu-1 kusiya ku -2  bengaluma abanye abantwana nxa bethukuthele ngokuthile. Ngokunjalo , kubalulekile  ukukhuluma ngesiqiniseko  uthi, \"Yekela ! Ukuluma kubuhlungu!\"\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EUngatshela abantwana ukuthi yini ongafisa beyenze esikhathini esizayo  . Ukududuza  umntwana olunyiwe lakho kubalulekile. Ngokuvamileyo abantwana asebekhulakhulile ,abalumi abanye. Nxa  umntwana  ethukuthele ,elendlela  yakhe yokuziphatha loba  elohlupho ekukhuleni  (njengokungathandi ukuxhumana labantu loma ukungakwazi ukukhuluma  ulimi lapho eleminyaka engu-3kusiya  ku-5), khuluma labezempilakahle  mayelana lokukukhathazayo.\u003C/p\u003E",
