            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EUkunaka kwakho lokudumisa kuqakathekile emntwaneni , njalo isikhathi esiningi lokhu kuyisisusa/intshukuntshu  eyaneleyo. Lapho abantwana bekhula ,bengathola intshukuntshu  ngokubona  impumela    yokuziphatha kuhle kwabanye. Ngokwesibonelo, ungathi, “Khangela  indlela udadewenu omncane ajabule ngayo.\u003C/p\u003E",
