            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EInengi labantwana bakhula  kahle nxa izinto empilweni yabo  zenzeka ngendlela abangayizwisisa lokulandela kalula. Kuwo wonke amasiko, kukhona indlela ezehlukeneyo zokuhlela okungenziwa ukuchitha isikhathi kwabantwana lamanye amalunga emuli . Kodwa  ke , kuhle ukuhlela imisebenzi ngesikhathi esifanayo malanga onke ,njengesikhathi sokulala, ukudla, ukudlala, njalo njalo. Abantwana abancane bazatshengisela  nxa sebefuna  ukudla, ukulala, njalo njalo. Kumaviki okuqala,lenyanga zakuqala umntwana uba lendlela ethile  yokwenza izinto ecacayo ngokuyakwesikhatthi .\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003E Abantwana asebekhulile kufanele bebekwazi abangakhangelela ukukwenza ngamalanga athile  Yiqiniso, ekuphileni kuzaba lezinto ezintsha ,kubalulekile ukuzama ukwenza impilo yomntwana wakho ibe lula futhi ilande le indlela ethile  ejwayelekileyo\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENxa umntwana elokukhubazeka kwezokuxhumana, okomzwelo, kumbe okokucabanga, inhlelo ezicacileyo zingamnceda. Ungayenza  inhlelo ezilula  usebemzisa imifanekiso lilonke   lomntwana . Ungakhombela  izinto  ezisehlelweni  (njengomfanekiso wombheda) ukukhombisa okulandelayo okuzayenzakala.\u003C/p\u003E",
