            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-17T09:54:05+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 03/17/2026 - 09:54\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EUkumunyisa uchago lukamama  kuphela  kungela okunye okudliwayo lokunathwayo) kuyakhuthazwa okwenyanga eziyisithupha zakuqala . Ngemva kwezinyanga eziyisithupha, ukumunyisa  umntwana esethola okunye  okudliwayo kuyakhuthazwa okweminyaka emibili kusedlula  kusiya ngokuthanda kwakho lomntwana. Ngemva kwalokho, wena lomntwama  lingaqhubeka lithola  inzuzo yokumunyisa okwesikhathi eside elingasifisa.Kuqakathekile njalo kuhle ukuthi umntwana amunye ngapha ethola okunye ukudla  okulomsoco  okweminyaka emibili kusedlula \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EKusukela kunyanga eziyisithupha ,amandla adingwa ngumntwana  aya esiba manengi okudlula lawo mandla atholakala kuchago lukamama kuphela. Ukumunyisa ngesikhathi umntwana eseqalise ukuphiwa okunye ukudla (okweminyaka emibili kuseldula) kuqhubeka kusipha amandla ,ama\u003Cem\u003E-fats , \u003C/em\u003E ama-\u003Cem\u003Eproteins\u003C/em\u003E kanye lo V\u003Cem\u003Eitamin \u003C/em\u003EA  \u003C/p\u003E",
