            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-17T09:54:05+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 03/17/2026 - 09:54\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EAkukho okungathatha indawo yochago lukamama njalo  akukho okunye ukudla kwabantwana okungaqhathaniswa lochago lukamama! Ukumunyisa uchago kulenzuzo ezinengi kuwe lomntwana  esikhathini esifitshane lakwelizayo . Okokuqala, uchago lukamama lunceda  ukugcina umntwana ephilile ngoba lunika umntwana zonke izakhamzimba/imisoco edingekayo ngesilinganiso esifaneleyo, luvikele ekungenweni yizinto ezithile, ekuguleni, njalo abantwana abamunyileyo  balamathuba amancane okukhuluphala kakhulu ebuntwaneni kanye lasekukhuleni. Ngaphezu kwalokho, uchago luvikela emikhuhlaneni , lugayeka lula, njalo abantwana baba lesisindo somzimba  esifaneleyo ekukhuleni kwabo\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EOkunye,nxa umntwana ekhula ,uchago lwakho luyatshintsha kuhambelana lezidingo zomntwana .Lutshintsha ubunengi lokumunyethweyo  kusiya ngokuthi umntwana umunya kangaki ,leminyaka yakhe ukuze akhule kuhle  Ngakho-ke, uchago lukamama luyikudla okupheleleyo komntwana. Ukumunyisa  kuthuthukisa  ingqondo kuncedise ekucabangaeni lakunkumbulo njalo kulenzuzo empilweni kamama.\u003C/p\u003E",
