            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EImithi yokuvikela imikhuhlane ilungisela okwenzakala nxa umzimba ungahlaselwa ligcikwane(virus and bacteria) kodwa ayisenzi sigule . Lapho imithi yokuvikela imikhuhlane ithontiselwa  kumbe ihlatshwa ,amagcikwane la angela mandla kumbe abuleweyo ayenza umzimba wazi ukuyenza amasothsa omzimba azalwa lemikhuhlane \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EUmzimba uzabamba ungasakhohlwa ukuthi ulwa njani lamagcikwane  Esikhathini esizayo,  nxa umzimba ungahlangana legcikwane eliphilayo futhi elilamandla uzakhumbula njalo uphange ukulwisana lalo ilibulale ,ngaphambi kokuba ungakaguli.  Ngakho-ke  ukuhlatshwa lokuthontiselwa  imithi yokuvikela  imikhuhlane kuyindlela ephephileyo yokuyenza amasothsa omzimba  okungabangeli ukugula \u003C/p\u003E",
