            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EUkuhlatshwa lokuthontiselwa  imithi yokuvikela imikhuhlane  kusindisa impilo  njalo kunceda  ukuthi abantwana bakhule kuhle  Kubavikela  emikhuhlaneni  engaletha impumela  emibi kakhulu egoqela ukukhubazeka  loba ukufa, ikakhulukazi ebantwini  abalamasotsha omzimba afana labantwana.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EKuqakathekile  uhlabisa lokuthontiselisa umntwana imithi evikela imikhuhlane  . Nxa kungenjalo, lapho ukuqubuka imikhuhlane ethelelanwayo,kubeka wena lomntwana kanye  labanye engozini.  Abantwana abangahlatshwanga basengozini enkulu yokuthola imikhuhlane eyingozi, njenge Measles, engabangela ubuphofu  ngitsho lokufa,  loba i polio okungabangela  ukhubazeka okungaqondisekiyo  kanye  lokufa.\u003C/p\u003E",
