            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EYebo, kuyelapheka. Kodwa abantu abanengi kabatholi ukunakekelwa abakudingayo ngenxa yokubandlululwa okuhambisana lokugula kwengqondo. Ukubandlululwa yikho lapho umuntu ephethe umbono omubi ngomunye ngenxa yokuthi lowo muntu ubonakala “ehlukile”\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EAbantu abagulayo engqondweni bavame ukubizwa ngamabizo amabi njalo behlulelwe. Ngenxa yalokho, abantu abanengi kabafuni ukuvuma ukuthi abaphilanga kuhle engqondweni  ngoba besaba ukubizwa ngamabizo amabi lokwahlulelwa\u003C/p\u003E",
