            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EUbudlelwano obugcwele uthando, obuzinzileyo  phakathi kwakho lomntwana buyisisekelo sokuthuthuka komntwana. Ngobudlelwano , abantwana bafunda indlela yokucabanga, yokuzwisisa , yokuxhumana, yokuziphatha, yokubonisa imizwa kanye lokuthuthukisa ukuxhumana labanye emphakathini.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
