            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EUkulungela isikolo kugoqela   ukulungela ngokomzimba (impilakahle yomzimba), ukulungela ngokwemizwa lokuziphatha emphakathini (ukwenza izinto labanye , ukuzwisisa  lokulawula imizwa), ukulungela ngolimi (ukukhuluma kanye lokulalela abanye), kanye lokunye okunjalo. Imisebenzi yakho yansuku zonke lobudlelwano olabo lomntwana kuyamnceda  kakhulu ekwakheni lokhu “kulungela isikolo.”\u003C/p\u003E",
