            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EAbantwana badinga ukudla kuwo wonke amaqembu ayisitshiyagalombili okudla okulempilakahle :\u003C/p\u003E\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003Eokusanhlamvu, impande  kanye lezilimo eziyizigaqa,\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EIzithelo lemibhida okule-Vitamin A,\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003Eezinye izithelo lemibhida ,\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003Eamaqanda,\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003Euchago\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003Enyama,\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003Eokucacadwayo\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003Euchago lukamama.\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ol\u003E\u003Cp\u003EUkudla  okulempilakahle kulemisoco eqakathekileyo  ekukhuleni komntwana lasekufundeni \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EUmntwana engadli ukudla okulesawudo elinengi, amafutha  kumbe itshukela ,,ukudla okungela sikuba,kudla okugayiwe kakhulu lokunathwayo okule-caffeine letshukela elinengi.\u003C/p\u003E",
