            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-07T15:56:53+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ESat, 03/07/2026 - 15:56\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-17T09:47:31+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 03/17/2026 - 09:47\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EEzinye izinto okufanele uzinanzele\u003C/p\u003E\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003EAbabalisi bakhuluma labantwana besebenzisa indlela yokuziphatha elothando lokukhuthaza.\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EAbantwana bachitha isikhathi esinengi bedlala futhi behlola izinto zangempela, hatshi nje ukwenza ama-workbook kumbe ukulolonga ukubhala.\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EAbantwana bachitha isikhathi bekumaqembu amancane, hatshi ukufunda bonke ndawonye ekilasini elikhulu malanga onke.\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EKukhona ama-toys kanye lezinye izinto ezaneleyo ukuze abantwana bawasebenzise, bayabelane, futhi bethabile.\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ol\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E\u003Col start=\"5\"\u003E\u003Cli\u003EAmakilasi kanye lendawo zokudlalela zihlanzekile futhi zibukeka zingekho yingozi ukuze abantwana bazisebenzise.\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EAbabalisi bakhangela abantwana nxa bedlala njalo bakhuthaze ukufunda kwabo kanye lokudlala ngokubambisana.\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ol\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAkula\u003Cem\u003E preschool\u003C/em\u003E epheleleyo ekwenzeni izinto ngendlela, kodwa lezi zindlela ezimbalwa ezizakwenza wazi ukuthi  i-\u003Cem\u003Epreschool\u003C/em\u003E \u003Cstrong\u003Eilohlonzi. \u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
            "chatbot_subcategory": 536,
