            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003ENxa kunzima kuwe ukuthenga amabhuku, zama ukubona ukuthi ungawathola yini ebanganeni kumbe kubomakhelwane abangabelana lawe amabhuku ,ababewasebenzisa ngesikhathi abantwana babo besebancane. Kuyenzeka njalo ukwenza amabhuku alula amancane; ungabhala udwebe izindaba zakho wena ngokwakho, kumbe uthathe imifanekiso kumaphephandaba kumbe kumamagazini ubumbe indaba ngazo.\u003C/p\u003E",
