            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EImpilo inzima emzalini ohlala exakekile kakhulu. Lanxa kunjalo, ukudlala kubalulekile ekukhuleni lasekufundeni komntwana. Kubalulekile futhi njengendlela yokuyakha ubudlelwano phakathi kwakho lomntwana. Zikhona indlela zokudlala lomntwana lanxa ukhathele. Ngokwesibonelo, mhlawumbe unganika umntwana izinto ezithile ezivela ekhitshini (inkezo, iinkomishi) kumbe imiqamelo ibe yinqwaba ukuze lenze “indlu” encane.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EUngahlala kumbe ulale eduze njalo ubuke umntwana ejabulela ukusondelana kwakho njalo uyathola ukuphumula. Mhlawumbe ungatshaya ingoma epholileyo ukuze  umntwana akwazi ukugida njalo ahlabele, lawe ukholise ingoma uhlabelele.\u003C/p\u003E",
