            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EZimbalwa kakhulu izizathu zempilakahle ezingenza umntwana angahlatshwa ngesikhathi esifaneleyo. Nxa abantwana bekhwehlela okujwayelakileyo kumbe besebenzisa ama-\u003Cem\u003Eantibiotics\u003C/em\u003E, bengahlatshwa nje, ukuhlatshwa lokhu akulangozi njalo kuyanceda kakhulu. Nxa umntwana etshisa umzimba kakhulu, abezempilakahle bengakhuthaza ukuhlatshwa komntwana ngemva kwesikhatshana. \u003C/p\u003E",
