            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-17T09:56:01+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 03/17/2026 - 09:56\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003ENxa  umntwana elokhu ekhula, mhlawumbe eseqala i -preschool  , eseqala ukuhlangana labanyee emphakathini,kudingeka afunde imithetho ethile mayelana labantu angabaziyo. Ungakwenza njani lokhu ungamesabisi ngabo bonke abantu aqala ukubabona ? Okokuqala, kubalulekile ukuqinisekisa ukuthi umntwana uyakwazi ukuthi umsebenzi wabazali bakhe yikumvikela ezingozini,egcineke kuhle. Ukumnakekela kwakho kumvikela ezintweni  ezinengi eziyingozi. Akufanelanga utshiye umntwana labantu ongabaziyo.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EUngafundisa njalo umntwana  ose -preschool ukuthi “umuntu ongaziwayo” ngubani — okutsho umuntu ongaziwa ngumntwana . Imithetho elula, njengokuthi angaze wahamba yedwa lomuntu  angamaziyo, lanxa lowo muntu esithi uyabazi abazali bakhe  kumbe emnika iziwiji , kungafundiswa lokuzilolonga ngokuxoxa izindaba, odoli, kumbe ama-puppet  ozenzele wona \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
