            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-17T09:56:01+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 03/17/2026 - 09:56\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003ENxa kungakabi lochago ngemva kwamalanga angu -3 kusiya kwang- 4 ngemva kokubeletha ,umntwana kufanele akhuthazwe ukumunya kanengi, kanti wena kufanele ukhiphe uchago lonke emabeleni  ngokupheleleyo  ngokumunyisa. Ukuyenza  \u003Cem\u003E(\u003Cstrong\u003Eskin-to-skin contact\u003C/strong\u003E)\u003C/em\u003E kunganceda ukwehla kochago emabeleni . Kuqakathekile   ukuthi umntwana aphathwe ngendlela eqondileyo njalo axhunywe kuhle ebeleni. Isisindo somzimba  womntwana siyalandelelwa  ukubona ukuthi kayehli  yini .Ukuqala ukumunyisa  kungaba nzima, kodwa inengi labesifazane bayaphumelela ngokuhamba kwesikhathi  ukwehlisa uchago kuze kufike  kusilinganiso esidingwa ngumntwana kuviki lakuqala  kusiya kwangu-2, kusiya  kumaviki ambalwa. Umntwana  nxa emunya  kanengi nengi njalo  akhiphe uchago ebeleni, uchago lwenziwa ngobunengi,uyehlise.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EKukhona izibonakaliso ezitshengisa  ukuthi umntwana  katholi uchago olwaneleyo. Ngokwesibonelo, umntwana akasuthanga  njalo uyagula ngemva kokumunya, uvuka masinyane, ufuna ukumunya kanengi nengi futhi okwe isikhathi eside,  njalo kamanzisi izisthubo ezifika-6 kumbe ukuphumela ka-2  ngelanga (ngemva kweviki yakuqala) njalo kangezeleleki isisindo somzimba \u003C/p\u003E",
