            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-17T09:56:01+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 03/17/2026 - 09:56\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003ENxa usazi  ukuthi umntwana ulokukhubazeka thize ulakho ukukhathazeka ngendlela akhula ngayo.Yebo Kunjalo! Kodwa ke khumbula ukuthi umntwana uyamangalisa ,ungumuntu omncane olendlela yakhe yokukhula .Kungayehlukana kumntwana munye ngamunye kodwa ke umntwana uzakhula ngoncedo lwakho!\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EAbezempilakahle kumbe umbalisi womntwana bengakuncedisa ukuhlela  indlela zokusekela umntwana kumisebenzi lemidlalo yakhe yansuku zonke. Ungazama njalo ukubona ukuthi umntwana yikuphi   akukwanisa ngcono (mhlawumbe akafundi izinto ngokuphangisa  kodwa uyazama nxa kunzima kumbe uyathakazelela ukubalelwa izindaba.Nanzelela lokho akwenza ngcono ,umncome ,ubusumnika indlela ezinye ezinengi zokwenza imisebenzi le.Lapho umntwana alobunzima kikho ,ungazama ukwenza imidlalo exwayiswa yi Rerai Umntwana ukuze ukhuthaze  ukwenza ngcono .Isibonelo, nxa umntwana elohlupho ekusebenziseni izandla , zama imidlalo ongayidlala, njengokudlulisa  lijikelane into elombala okhanyayo\u003C/p\u003E",
