            "type": "FAQ",
            "question": "Ngingagcina  njani umntwana exhumene labanye ngesikhathi se-COVID?",
            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-06T04:48:56+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EFri, 03/06/2026 - 04:48\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-17T09:56:01+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 03/17/2026 - 09:56\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EKuhle ukuthi ufuna ukuthi uhlale uxhumene lomntwana    ngesikhathi lapho lingekho ndawonye.Imuli ezinengi zisebenzisa ama-phone ukwenza ama video nge Whatsapp  lokunye okunjalo. Laloba umntwana esamncane kakhulu ,uyakukhangela ku video,azwe ilizwi  lakho athole ukujabula.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EMhlawumbe  abantwana bengatshengisa ugogo lokhulu imifanekiso abayidwebileyo  kumbe amathoyi  abawathandisisayo. Ezinye izindlela zokuhlala uxhumene zihlanganisa ukubuka izithombe ndawonye, ukubhala incwadi ndawonye, mhlawumbe  lifake isithombe phakathi kumbe lokuxoxa nje ngemuli.\u003C/p\u003E",
