            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-05T21:28:58+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EThu, 03/05/2026 - 21:28\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-17T09:56:01+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 03/17/2026 - 09:56\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EYebo, lokhu  yinto engenzeka . Xoxisana  labe-pre school ngomehluko wolimi, libuze ukuthi isikolo singancedisa  njani umntwana afunde ulimi lwabo olutsha besahlonipha ulimi lwangekhaya. Ngokuvamileyo kuhle kakhulu ukuthi abantwana babekwazi indimi  ezimbili.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EUngasekela umntwana ukufunda indimi zombili\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EAbantwana bafunda indimi ezintsha kalula kakhulu ukwedlula thina abantu abadala! Ama-preschool amahle,amqoka  akhuthaza abantwana ukuthi basebenze futhi badlale ndawonye ngesikhathi besesikolo. Ngalezo zikhathi, umntwana  angaqala ukufunda amazwi alula ,lemitsho elula ngolimi olutsha.Umbalisi  womntwana  kumele abe lezinye izindlela zokwenza umntwana azizwe ekhululekile njalo akhule kancane kancane ekuzethembeni ekusebenziseni ulimi olutsha.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
