            "type": "FAQ",
            "question": "Yiphi imihlobo yokudlala elungele abantwana? ",
            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-05T21:26:34+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EThu, 03/05/2026 - 21:26\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-03-17T09:56:01+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 03/17/2026 - 09:56\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003ENxa ubuka abantwana , uzababona bedlala ngendlela ezinengi. Zonke lezi ndlela zingabanceda abantwana ukufunda! Kwesinye isikhathi abantwana bayagijima, beseqa  njalo begada izinto . Lokhu kudlala kwakha  ukusebenza komzimba.Nxa abantwana bedlala ngokulingisa (okufana lokwenza sengathi ilembu yingubo  kumbe isiqephu sokhuni yifoni), abantwana bathuthukisa ukucabanga lobuciko .\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003ENxa abantwana  bedweba imifanekiso kumbe bezama ukubhala amabizë abo, bayakha ukuqala ukufunda lokubhala (early literacy skills). Nxa abantwana bedlala labangane , bayafunda ukuthi bangasebenzisana njani labanye kanye lokuthi bangenzani  nxa kulengxabano.Lezi ndlela zokudlala ziyizibonelo ezimbalwa zemihlobo  yemidlalo  ezingancedisa abantwana  ukufunda futhi bazilungiselele ukuphumelela  esikolo .\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
