            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EYebo, lukhona uncedo njalo ithemba lokuphila lihlala likhona. Nxa umuntu ezizwa ngalendlela, kubalulekile kakhulu ukuthi angahlali yedwa. Kumele afinyelele masinyane emuntwini amthembayo—kungaba yilunga lemuli, umngane oqotho, kumbe owezempilakahle. Ngenxa yokukhathazeka kakhulu enqgondweni, ukudangala (\u003Cem\u003Edepression\u003C/em\u003E), ukuhlukumezeka (\u003Cem\u003Etrauma\u003C/em\u003E) ohlangana lakho sungazizwa ngalendlela.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EKodwa nxa wena, kumbe othile emulini, ozizwa ngalendlela, qiniseka ukuthi uyaluthola uncedo. Ukuhlala uphilile engqondweni kubalulekile kuwe, ebantwaneni bakho lasemulini. Nxa ungaphilanga kuhle kuphambanisa indlela owondla ngayo abantwana. Dinga usizo, uncedakale! Ungathintana  le-\u003Cem\u003EDepartment of Social Development\u003C/em\u003E (wonke amahofisi e-\u003Cem\u003EProvince\u003C/em\u003E le-\u003Cem\u003Edistrict\u003C/em\u003E) and \u003Cem\u003EMusasa Project toll-free numbers \u003C/em\u003E(\u003Cem\u003E08080074, 0731080072, 0731080074\u003C/em\u003E).\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
            "chatbot_subcategory": 626,
            "related_article": 2776,
            "mandatory": 1
