            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003ELomntwana lingabonisana ndawonye ngalokho elingakwenza kanye lokuchaza ukuziphatha okufunayo. Nxa umntwana elobudlelwano lawe, ekhwethemba, njalo ethanda ukuba lawe, uzafuna ukukujabulisa ngokuziphatha kahle.\u003C/p\u003E",
