            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EAkudingeki ukuthi “ufundise” umntwana, njengoba ezafunda ukubala nxa esesiya esikolo. Kodwa, phose yonke into oyenzayo ngekhaya inganceda umntwana ukuthi alungele ukubala kahle ngokuhamba kwesikhathi.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EUkuxoxa labantwana ngezinto ezijwayelekileyo kumbe ukubabalela kuzangezelela uluhlu lwamabala abazawasebenzisa nxa sebebala. Ukukhombela izinto nxa ukhuluma labantwana kuzayenza bazwisise ngcono ibala lokukhombelayo. Okuqakatheke kakhulu yikunika umntwana uthando lokubala lokumenza athakazelele ukubala lamabala, imisindo, amabhuku lezindaba.\u003C/p\u003E",
