            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EUkungaliseki engqondweni/Ukucabangisisa kakhulu kungabonakala ngezitshengiselo ezilandelayo \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003EUkudabuka okukhulu\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EUkungakwazi ukuzwa ubumnandi\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EUbunzima bokugxilisa ingqondo\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EUkukhuphuka kumbe ukuncipha kakhulu kwesifiso sokudla kanye lesisindo somzimba\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EUkudinwa kumbe ukwanda okukhulu kumbe ukuncipha kwesikhathi esichithwa ulele\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EImizwa eyedlulele, umuzwa wecala kanye lokungabi yinto yalutho\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EUkuzizwa ungelathemba futhi ungela ndlela yokuzisiza. \u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ul\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EEzimweni ezimbi kakhulu, lezi zitshengiselo zokungahlaliseki engqondweni /ukucabangisisa kakhulu zingahambisana lemicabango yokuzibulala kumbe ukuzama ukuzibulala. Ngokungahlaliseki engqondweni , isimo sengqondo somuntu sihlala siphansi amalanga onke kusiya kumaviki. Lesi simo esibuhlungu sithinta indlela yokwenza imisebenzi yansuku zonke.\u003C/p\u003E",
