            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EMinengi imithi/amajekiseni avunyelwa yi-WHO kanye le-\u003Cem\u003EMedicines Control Authority of Zimbabwe (MCAZ) \u003C/em\u003Eukuthi ihlatshwe abantwana abaleminyaka emithathu (3) kusiya phezulu. I-Zimbabwe yaqala ukuhlaba ijekiseni ye-\u003Cem\u003ECOVID-19\u003C/em\u003E kubantwana abaleminyaka engu-12 kusiya ku 17 kudala ngo-2021 kanye labaleminyaka engu-3 kusiya ku 11 ngo-2022. Sicela uthintane labezempilakahle ukuthola imibiko emitsha mayelana laloludaba. \u003C/p\u003E",
