            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EUngalugcina uchago lwakho njalo ulusebenzise lapho kudingeka, ukuze ungancitshi umntwana ukudla lokhu okumqoka. Uchago olusengwe ngendlela lwagcinwa kahle alutshintshi njalo lulungele umntwana.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EKusiya ngezidingo zomntwana, ungenelisa ukunika umntwana uchago lolu olusengiweyo, ulugcine efrijini ukuze unike umntwana ngesikhathi esizayo, kumbe uluhambise emntwaneni (nxa lehlukanisiwe ngenxa yezinye izizathu). Landela izixwayiso zokugcina uchago lukamama olusengiweyo!\u003C/p\u003E",
