            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EUkubukela ku-TV kumbe i-phone  akukhuthazwa ebantwaneni abangaphansi kweminyaka engu-2(ngaphandle nxa kungama video-calls emuli).Ebantwaneni  abaphezu kweminyaka emibili kukhuthazwa  ihola elilodwa ngelanga ,lapho umntwana ebukela akukhethelweyo .Abantwana abancane kakhulu bafunda ngcono kakhulu kulokho okwenzakala emhlabeni wangempela njengokuyenza i -exercise , ukudlala phandle,  ukubala ,ukudlala ngokulinganisa,kanye lokuchitha isikhathi lemuli labangane \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EUngaba yisibonelo esihle semikhuba yokusebenzisa i-screen  emntwaneni. Lokhu kungaba yikufaka i-phone eceleni ngesikhathi sokudla njalo ungayisebenzisi nxa udlala lomntwana kumbe umunyisa kumbe umnika  ukudla . Qaphela lokho abantwana abakubukelayo ukuze ubavikele ukubukela izinto ezingabakhathaza kumbe ukubethusa.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
