            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EKukhona ukudangala lokukhathazeka ,ukucabangisisa kakhulu  okuhlangana lomama ngezikhathi ezithwele langemva kokubeletha . Lobanje ukuzalwa komntwana kubukeka njengesikhathi sokuthokoza okukhulu,kodwa ke abanye omama ,obaba lezimuli  isikhathi sokuzithwala langemva kokubeletha singaba yisikhathi sokukhathazeka lokudaleka kwenhlupho\u003C/p\u003E",
