            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EOkokuqala,  ukukhula komntwana akusiwona umncintiswano.Abantwana balezikhathi zabo ezehlukeneyo  lokuthuthuka ngokwemvelo, ngakho akufanelanga ujahe  umntwana ukuthi afinyelele ezingeni lokuthuthuka/ukukhula . Njalo okunye nje ukuthuthuka   (njengokuphakamisa ikhanda, ukugiqika, lokuhlala)  kuyazenzakalela nje ngokwemvelo ngesikhathi esikhangelelweyo. Akudingi  ukumfundisa umntwana !\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EKukhona nje abantwana abahlala bebonakala bephambili kulabontanga babo , ngokwesibonelo nxa umntwana eqala ukukhuluma ,ekubala , ekufundeni ukugada  ibhayisikili, njalo njalo. Kodwa laba bantwana  akutsho ukuthi balokuhlakanipha thize kumbe balobungcono ekukhuleni kwabo  kusikhathi esizayo. Kanengi, umntwana ophambili kancane kwenye indawo uba esemuva kwezinye izingxenye zokuthuthuka nxa  kuqhathaniswa labanye abantwana.\u003C/p\u003E",
