            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EAbantwana abanengi abazalwa isikhathi singakafiki  bayakhula njengabontanga babo  abazalwa ngesikhathi esigcweleyo. Kodwa  esikhathini esinengi  abantwana abazalwa isikhathi singakafiki baba lobunzima ekukhuleni .Amaprimitsha adinga uthando,lendawo enhle, ekhuthaza ukuthi umntwana akhule , ngekhaya kanye  lasesikolo, lapho  abantwana abazenelisa ukwakha ubudlelwano  ukuze bencediseke ekukhuleni\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
