            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EIphepha lamapenseli  loba  amakhrayoni kunceda umntwana   ukuthi afunde ubuciko njalo abhale okungaqondakaliyo okuzamncedisa ukuthi abhale amabala phambilini   Lezi yizibonelo ezimbalwa nje. Khumbula ukuthi amathoyi  akudingeki ukuba abize /adule ! Ungakwanisa njalo  ukutshintshanisa amathoyi labanye abazali  okwesikhatshana nxa abantwana sebedakakile ngawabo .\u003C/p\u003E",
