            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EAbantwana abancane bayathanda ukuhlola ngezandla .Bayadobha izinto bafake emlonyeni  ukuze bafunde ngezinto.Umsebenzi wakho yikunanzelela ukuthi izinto lezi zihlanzekile njalo azilimazi engazifakanga emlonyeni.Ungavumeli umntwana afake izinto emlonyeni  angaziginya zimkhame.Ngitsho  lezithelo ezinjengama grapes  kufanele ziqunywe zibe  zincezu ezincane .Ungavumeli umntwana ehlafuna amathoyi alependa ecucukayo ngoba ingaba le-poison.  \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003ENanzelela ukuthi umntwana nxa sehamba ,akafikeli izinto eziyingozi ezingamlimaza . Yebo, futhi qiniseka ukuthi izinto umntwana azifaka emlonyeni zihlanzekile.  Nxa unanzelela lokhu  , umntwana engazihlafunela izinto ezinengi azithakazelelayo. Khuluma  lomntwana ngalezi zinto : “O, le yinkomitshi enkulu ebomvu ! Uyafuna , ukuhlafuna isibambo?” Ngazo zonke lezi ndlela, unceda umntwana ukuthi afunde.\u003C/p\u003E",
