            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EUcabanga ukuthi  ngubani ithoyi yokuqala emntwaneni ? Nguwe! Ikakhulukazi kunyanga  zokuqala ,umntwana ufuna ukubona ubuso bakho , ukulalela ilizwi lakho, ukuthintana lomzimba wakho, lokufunda okunengi lawe.\u003C/p\u003E",
