            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EI-World Health Organization ithi, “impilo yisimo senhlalakahle epheleleyo yomzimba, inqondo ,lobudlelwano labanye ,hatshi nje ukuswelakala kwemikhuhlane lezifo .” Ukugula ingqondo kuthinta imizwa, imicabango kanye lokuziphatha kwabantu. Ukugula ingqondo kungaba  lempumela engekho mihle empilweni zabantu kanye lezimuli zabo \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EAbantu abagula  ingqondo bangabe  bengakwazi  kumbe belenhloni zokukhuluma ngakho . Lokhu kwenza kube nzima ukuthi bacele uncedo  njalo  bathole ukwelatshwa. Impilakahle  yengqondo ithinta impilo yomzimba. Isibonelo, umuntu ozizwa encindezelekile:,ekhathazeke kakhulu umoya wakhe uphansi ,: mhlawumbe ngeke athole uncedo aludingayo njalo usengozini yokuthi agule ngoba amasotsha omzimba awala mandla lokhu kube ngokumenza engenelisi ukunatha imithi okufanele inathwe.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "chatbot_subcategory": 636,
            "related_article": 3826,
            "mandatory": 1
