            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-25T21:32:12+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EWed, 02/25/2026 - 21:32\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-26T11:25:11+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EThu, 02/26/2026 - 11:25\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EIzitshengiselo zokugula ingqondo :\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003EUkutshintsha kwemizwa.\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EInguquko yendlela  umuntu abona ngayo izinto ezimqoka\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EUkutshintsha kwendlela umuntu agxilisa  ngayo imicabango yakhe.\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003E Ukutshintsha lokhu kungaphambanisa indlela abantu abangasebenza ngayo. Abantu abalohlupho  lwengqondo bakhangelana lalokhu okulandelayo:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003EUkungasebenzi kakhulu   emsebenzini.\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EUkungenelisi ukukhangelana  lenhlupho \u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EUkungenelisi ukuxhumana labanye abakusekelayo empilweni\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003EUkuze wazi ukuthi ulokukhathazeka emicabangweni lokudangala  bona abezempilakahle  \u003C/p\u003E",
