            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EKhulumani, hlabelani, dlalani njalo lifunde ndawonye malanga onke . Abantwana bafunda okunengi ngokuphatheka  emisebenzini yamalanga onke. Ngokwesibonelo, nxa uhamba lomntwana ukuyathenga ukudla, uzafunda amabala  amanengi ezithelo lemibhida , njalo lingakhuluma ngemibala ehlukeneyo yokudla.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EKusiya ngeminyaka lokuthakazelelwa ngumntwana,cabanga ngongakwenza okungancedisa umntwana ahlolisise izinto (njengokuthatha amahlamvu phandle liwahlukanise ngombala,lixazulule  okuhluphayo (ucabanga ukuthi ngicabanga ngayiphi inyamazana?) kumbe ukufunda ngenombolo  (njengokubala izipunu zokubeka etafuleni), kanye lokunye okunengi !\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
