            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003ENgokuvamileyo abantwana abazelwe isikhathi singakakwani  kufanele bathole imithi yokuvikela imikhuhlane njengabo bonke abantwana. Ngempela, kuqakathekile ukuthi abantwana abazelwe isikhathi singakakwani  bathole imithi yokuvikela imikhuhlane ngoba basengozini enkulu yemikhuhlane \u003C/p\u003E",
