            "question": "Indlela yokuvikela lokwenqabela  ukukhuluphala/ ukuba lesisindo esikhulu kakhulu ebantwaneni?",
            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-25T20:41:45+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EWed, 02/25/2026 - 20:41\u003C/time\u003E\n",
