            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EIndlela ezinengi zokuvikela ukukhuluphala kumbe ukuba lesisindo kakhulu zigoqela ukudla okulempilakahle, ukuyenza imisebenzi lemidlalo eqinisa umzimba (\u003Cem\u003Eexercise)\u003C/em\u003E kanye lokunciphisa isikhathi sokutshona ehlezi, engayenzi lutho njengokubukela i-TV lokudlala imidlalo ku -c\u003Cem\u003Eomputer. \u003C/em\u003EUkukhuluphala kakhulu kwesisindo somzimba ngokuvamileyo kubangelwa yikudla kakhulu kumbe ukungenzi i\u003Cem\u003E-exercise\u003C/em\u003E ngokwaneleyo.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EUkukhuluphala kudala imikhuhlane empilweni, yikho kufanele kuhlolwe kubonakale ,kulungiswe masinya. Nxa unanzelele ukuthi umntwana sengezeleleka isisindo somzimba kakhulu , hamba laye kwabezempilakahle ahlolisiswe ngokugcweleyo \u003C/p\u003E",
