            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EAsikho isizatho sokuyekela ukuhlabisa umntwana ngenxa yokwenziwa i-\u003Cem\u003Esurgery \u003C/em\u003Eokwedlulileyo kumbe okuzayo. Ukwenza i\u003Cem\u003E-surgery\u003C/em\u003E akusiso sizatho sokuyekela ukuthi umntwana ahlatshelwe ukuvikela imikhuhlane.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EImithi yokuvikela imikhuhlane iqinisa amasotsha omzimba omntwana njalo imvikela emikhuhlaneni eyingozi ennjenge ndingindi, ebangela ubuphofu kumbe ukufa.\u003C/p\u003E",
