            "question": "Ingabe i-preschool ilungele umntwana okhubazekileyo?",
            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-25T15:25:59+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EWed, 02/25/2026 - 15:25\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-26T11:25:11+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EThu, 02/26/2026 - 11:25\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003ENxa endaweni ohlala kuyo kule \u003Cem\u003Epre-school\u003C/em\u003E, kunganceda kakhulu ekuthuthukiseni ukukhula komntwana olokukhubazeka. Indawo yabontanga ilamandla amakhulu okuvusa intuthuko, ikakhulu nxa “ifaka bonke” (\u003Cem\u003Einclusive\u003C/em\u003E) njalo ihlanganisa ekilasini elilodwa abantwana abakhubazekileyo labangakhubazekanga. Ukuhlanganiswa lokhu kunganceda bonke abantwana.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003ENxa umntwana ekwanisa ukuya e-\u003Cem\u003Epreschool\u003C/em\u003E, xhumanisa umbalisi womntwana labezempilakahle. Abe zempilakahle bazakwazi ukuxwayisa indlela ezingcono zokuthi uhlelo lwe-\u003Cem\u003Epreschool\u003C/em\u003E lukhuthaze njalo luthuthukise ukukhula komntwana. Wena, lombalisi womntwana, kanye labezempilakahle lingaba liqembu elihle kakhulu elisebenza ndawonye!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
