            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003ENgaphambi kokuthatha loba yiwuphi umuthi ngesikhathi umunyisa, kuhle ngaso sonke isikhathi ukwazisa abezempilakahle ukuthi uyamunyisa. Abezempilakahle bazakukhethela umuthi kugoqela ama-\u003Cem\u003Eantibiotics \u003C/em\u003Eolungele ukuthi uwunathe ngesikhathi umunyisa umntwana.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
