            "type": "FAQ",
            "question": " Yiphi imikhuhlane evikelwa yimithi ehlatshwayo lethontiselwayo?",
            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-25T15:13:24+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EWed, 02/25/2026 - 15:13\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-26T11:25:11+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EThu, 02/26/2026 - 11:25\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EAma-\u003Cem\u003Evaccine\u003C/em\u003E avikela umntwana emkhuhlaneni eyingozi, enjenge-\u003Cem\u003Epolio\u003C/em\u003E, engabangela ukukhubazeka komzimba (\u003Cem\u003Eparalysis\u003C/em\u003E), kumbe i-\u003Cem\u003Emeasles\u003C/em\u003E, engabangela ukuvuvuka kobuchopho, ubuphofu, kumbe ukufa. Sebenzisa i-tool elama-\u003Cem\u003Evaccinations\u003C/em\u003E ku-\u003Cem\u003Eapp\u003C/em\u003E ukuze ubone okumayelana lama-\u003Cem\u003Evaccines \u003C/em\u003Eakhuthazwa elizweni le-Zimbabwe.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003ELandela uhlelo lwase-Zimbabwe lokuhlabisa lokuthontisela abantwana; njalo ungayeqisi kumbe ukuyekelisi ukuyahlabisa kumbe ukuthontiselisa umntwana lokhu okukhuthazwayo ngabezempilakahle. \u003C/p\u003E",
