            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EObaba baqakathekile kuzozonke izikhathi zokukhula komntwana. Abanye obaba abakujwayelanga ukuncedisa ekunakekeleni umntwana omncane kakhulu kodwa ngokukhuthaza kwakho, obaba bangaqalisa ukubamba, lokulolozela, ukugqokisa indodakazi kumbe indodana yabo encane. Kunganceda nxa umtshela ukuthi enzeni.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EUngamtshengisa ukuthi umntwana uyathaba ukumbona njalo aqale ukudlala lomntwana esebenzisa izinto ezilula. Khangelani ndawonye indlela umntwana akhula njalo afunda ngayo! Kwesinye isikhathi ngumlandu wakho ukunika ubaba isikhathi sokudlala lomntwana ngendlela yakhe. Omunye wakho angawondla umntwana ngendlela etshiyeneyo kuleyakho, kulungile lokho. Zama ukuthokoza ngalokho akwenzayo loba nje kutshiyene. Abantwana bakho bazazuza ngendlela zombili zokukhuliswa.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EUngamtshengisa ukuthi umntwana uyathaba ukumbona njalo aqale ukudlala lomntwana esebenzisa izinto ezilula. Khangelani ndawonye indlela umntwana akhula njalo afunda ngayo! Kwesinye isikhathi ngumlandu wakho ukunika ubaba isikhathi sokudlala lomntwana ngendlela yakhe. Omunye wakho angawondla umntwana ngendlela etshiyeneyo kuleyakho, kulungile lokho. Zama ukuthokoza ngalokho akwenzayo loba nje kutshiyene. Abantwana bakho bazazuza ngendlela zombili zokukhuliswa.\u003C/p\u003E",
