            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-25T15:00:02+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EWed, 02/25/2026 - 15:00\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-26T11:25:11+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EThu, 02/26/2026 - 11:25\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EImithi yokuthontisela lokuhlabisa abantwana inikwa masinya ukuze abantwana bavikeleke emikhuhlaneni lapho imizimba yabo isakhula njalo ibuthakathaka. Nxa engavikelekanga, umntwana uba sengozini yokuhlaselwa ngamagciwane ayingozi angaphambanisa impilakahle lokukhula kwakhe. Yingakho kubalulekile ukuhlabisa lokuthontiselisa abantwana ngesikhathi. Sicela uvakatshele Ithulu lokuthontiselwa lokuhlatshwa kwabantwana ukuze ufunde ngemithi okufanele inikwe umntwana ngesikhathi esithile.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EImithi yokuthontisela lokuhlabisa abantwana inikwa masinya ukuze abantwana bavikeleke emikhuhlaneni lapho imizimba yabo isakhula njalo ibuthakathaka. Nxa engavikelekanga, umntwana uba sengozini yokuhlaselwa ngamagciwane ayingozi angaphambanisa impilakahle lokukhula kwakhe. Yingakho kubalulekile ukuhlabisa lokuthontiselisa abantwana ngesikhathi. Sicela uvakatshele Ithulu lokuthontiselwa lokuhlatshwa kwabantwana ukuze ufunde ngemithi okufanele inikwe umntwana ngesikhathi esithile.\u003C/p\u003E",
