            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-26T11:25:11+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EThu, 02/26/2026 - 11:25\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EIzibonakaliso zokungahambelani kancane lokudla okuthile zigoqela ukuqubuka, ukuvuvuka, ukulunywa emlonyeni, ubuhlungu besisu, ukuhlanza kanye lesihudo. Izibonakaliso zokuhambelani kakhulu lokudla okuthile kumbe ukugula zigoqela ukuvaleka komphimba, ukuphefumula nzima kanye lokuqaleka.  \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EBona abezempilakahle ukuze uhlolisiswe ngokugcweleyo ngokudla okuthile ongahambelani lakho. Abantwana akufanelanga badle ukudla okuthile abangahambelani lakho. Nxa besengozini yokugula, kungadingeka ukuthwala i-\u003Cem\u003Eadrenaline auto-injector\u003C/em\u003E.\u003C/p\u003E",
