            "type": "FAQ",
            "question": "Ngingancedisa njani umntwana ukuthi akhule/athuthuke? ",
            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-25T14:21:51+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EWed, 02/25/2026 - 14:21\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-02-26T11:25:11+01:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EThu, 02/26/2026 - 11:25\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EKulezinto ezinengi, ezilula kodwa eziqakathekileyo kakhulu ongazenza ukuncedisa umntwana ukuthi akhule eminyakeni yokuqala ezigoqela:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Col\u003E\u003Cli\u003EUkusabela imisindo, ukunyakaza, ukukhala kanye lokuthandwa ngumntwana ngendlela efaneleyo: nxa umntwana efisa ukuthatha into ethile, uyamnika, abeseyibuyisela kuwe.\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EUkududuza umntwana nxa edanile kuyanceda ukwakha isisekelo esiqinileyo sokuzizwa evikelekile.\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ol\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003E3. Ukupha umntwana izinto ezilula zokudlalisa, okuncedisa ukuvusa ingqondo yakhe.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E4. Ukukhuluma, ukubala, lokuhlabela lomntwana nsuku zonke, kuncedisa ingqondo yakhe ilungiselele ukukhuluma, ukubala lokubhala!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E5. Ukudlala imidlalo lomntwana kuqakathekile ekuthuthukiseni ingqondo yakhe.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
