            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EOkunye ukukhubazeka, okufana le-\u003Cem\u003Eautism spectrum\u003C/em\u003E, kwenza kube nzima kakhulu ebantwaneni ukuhlala bethule ezimweni ezibakhathazayo. Abanye abantwana bayacaphuka kakhulu nxa kusiba lenguquko encane nje emikhubeni yabo yamalanga onke, baze bakhale kumbe bethukuthele. Abantwana abalokukhubazeka kwengqondo, njengalabo abale-\u003Cem\u003Edown syndrome\u003C/em\u003E, bangabonisa ukusilela ekuziphatheni ngenxa yobunzima bokusebenzisa amazwi, kumbe ngenxa yokungaqondi kuhle okukhangelelweyo kubo.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EAbazempilakahle bangakunika imibono ngendlela ezingakunceda. Ngokwesibonelo, inhlelo ezilula ezilezithombe zingatshela umntwana okukhangelelwe kuye. Ungadinga ukwehlukanisa umsebenzi onzima ube ngamanyathelo amancane, weluleke umntwana ekwenzeni lokhu. Bonisa abantwana ukuthi uyazwisisa ubunzima abakhangelane labo lokuthi uyabathanda njalo uyabasekela.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
