            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EAbantwana bafunda izinto ezinengi ngesikhathi bedlala. Ngakho-ke, nxa ubancitsha isikhathi sokudlala, abafundi kangako. Kodwa-ke, nxa umntwana eqamula amathoyi kumbe etshaya omunye umuntu ngesikhathi edlala, kudingeka ukuthi umise lokho kuziphatha. Thatha ithoyi ngokuthula, chaza isizatho, uthole enye into umntwana angadlala ngayo engamlimaziyo, wena umkhangele .\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003ENgemva kwesikhathi ungababonisa ukuthi basebenzise amazwi ukuveza izifiso zabo. Khumbula ukuthi abantwana basesebancane kakhulu. Abantwana badinga ukuthi ubafundise indlela yokuziphatha, ukuze baqhubeke befunda ngokudlala.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E",
