            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EUkwenza imisebenzi lemidlalo eqinisa umzimba ukuthi ubelempilakahle kanye lenhlalakahle . Kodwa-ke ama-\u003Cem\u003Elockdown\u003C/em\u003E lama-\u003Cem\u003Equarantine\u003C/em\u003E ayaphambanisa lokhu. Nxa uthanda ukugida, dlala ingoma efonini yakho.\u003C/p\u003E",
