            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EYour young children learn from you every day, when you talk with them, play simple games, draw pictures together, take them for walks around your neighbourhood, sing and tell or read stories all of these and other activities are “teaching” without being a teacher.\u003C/p\u003E",
