            "answer_part_1": "\u003Cp\u003EAbantwana bayesaba njalo abalawuleki lapho besenzya ama-tantrumsa . Ngalesi sikhathi esinzima (ukuklabalala, ukukhala, ukuwela phansi.), ukubonisana  lomntwana ngeke kuncede ,njalo ukumjezisa kungamane kuyenze umntwana angezelele ukwenzya ama-tantrums . Ungaqinisekisa abantwana kuthi ukhona njalo uzamncedisa  ukwehlise umoya. Wazi kangcono  umntwana wakho: mhlawumbe  ukuhlala laye phansi kumbe ukumnika  i i thoyi ayithandayo  ukuthi ayibambe.\u003C/p\u003E",
            "answer_part_2": "\u003Cp\u003EMhlawumbe ubakhumbuza izindlela ezithile  zokwehlisa umoya. Ungatshiye  umntwana ekhala. Yehlisa umoya,uhlale lomntwana  umsondeze eduze. Lokhu kutshengisa  ukuthi uyaqonda njalo uyakwazi ukuphatha loba yiphi imizwa yabo. Umtshele uthi  “Kulungile ukudabuka, ukuthukuthela, ukwesaba. Ngikhona laphaukukweseka.” Okokucina, khuluma labezempilakahle  nxa  ukucasuka lokhu kungezelela kusiba nzima ukukulawula, ikakhulukazi labantwana asebekhulakhulile.\u003C/p\u003E",
